    <description>User Summary.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This module rounds out the game to become a complete package for WW2 small unit simulation.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Adds on the last of the armour from 1944-45 including the IS2, M24 Chaffee, M26 Pershing, PzIVJ, Koenigstiger and Crab.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Addition to the basic rules include; &amp;#10;Spaced Armour immunity to HEAT based weapons, &amp;#10;High velocity guns no longer benefiting from falling shots at extreme ranges, &amp;#10;The additional carnage of multiple barrelled weapons and &amp;#10;The devestating power of rocket artillery.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The platoon roster have now been replaced with nation specific versions including early (rifles) and late (assault rifles and LMGS) versions for Germany.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The major update to the system is the inclusion of what the designers call a 'Box Wars' points sysem for competitive play. This adds a meticulous costing system to every item already included in the game. This is particularly useful for the more casual gamer who is not looking to recreate a specific action.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The five new scenarios are very well presented and now include a useful General Situation, Commanders' briefings and Umpire notes.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
